	"description": "Microinteractions guide a user through your application. They reinforce your\nuser experience and provide delight.\n\nYou may have seen some of the slick examples of microinteractions on Dribble\n[https://dribbble.com/search?q&#x3D;microinteraction] or CodePen\n[https://codepen.io/search/pens?q&#x3D;microinteraction&amp;limit&#x3D;all&amp;type&#x3D;type-pens].\nBut do you know how to build your own library of similar UI widgets?\n\nIn this article, I’ll focus on animated microinteractions using React\n[https://facebook.github.io/re",
